energy future intermediate holding co llc / efih finance inc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Utilities
Industry: Utilities
Sub-Industry: Integrated Utilities
Energy Future Intermediate Holding Co LLC / EFIH Finance Inc. operates as a special purpose entity that issues debt. The Company was set up in order to raise capital for the funding of general business purposes.




