Preliminary
Adjusted EBITDA (as defined below) for the twelve months ended
June 30, 2010 and 2009 totaled $5,116 million and $4,689
million, respectively. 

 


 


EFH Corp.
management continues to evaluate the effect of declining wholesale
power prices, due to lower natural gas prices, on the carrying
value of goodwill related to the TCEH reporting unit. This
evaluation may ultimately result in the recording of a non-cash
goodwill impairment charge. Such charge, if any, would be recorded
no sooner than in the three month period ended September 30,
2010.

