from Asset Sales of Oncor-related Assets) by (b) a fraction,
the numerator of which shall be the sum of the aggregate principal
amount of the EFH Corp. 9.75% Notes, the EFH Corp. 10.000% Notes
and any other Parity Lien Debt of EFH Corp. that is guaranteed by
EFIH pursuant to clause (2) of Section 4.09(b) hereof and
the denominator of which shall be the aggregate principal amount of
(i) the EFH Corp. 9.75% Notes, the EFH Corp. 10.000% Notes and
any other Parity Lien Debt of EFH Corp. that is guaranteed by EFIH
plus (ii) the Notes, any Additional Notes, any Exchange Notes,
the EFIH 9.75% Notes, any additional EFIH 9.75% Notes, the EFIH
10.000% Notes, any additional EFIH 10.000% Notes and any other
Parity Lien Debt of EFIH, in the case of clauses (i) and
(ii) incurred pursuant to clause (2) of
Section 4.09(b) hereof and at the time outstanding.

